    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in 'as-is' condition and is best suited for someone looking for a project or a parts car. The engine currently has significant oil leaks and a noticeable knock, and the transmission slips when shifting into higher gears. Cosmetically, the body shows heavy rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, while the interior has multiple tears in the upholstery and a non-functional AC system. It will likely require a tow and substantial mechanical work to be roadworthy again.",
